../execution-framework/reviews/GPT55_REQ027_APPROVAL_REVIEW.md:1:{"decision":"approved","reason":"REQ-027_ENVCTL_REPLAY_ENGINE may be unlocked for agent execution. REQ-026 is complete with passing rollback-checkpoint smoke coverage and checksum-bound proof evidence, REQ-027's declared dependencies are complete, the scheduler currently blocks REQ-027 only on the agent approval artifact, and the approval gate remains fail-closed by requiring a valid approval record, review artifact, fallback reason for GPT-5.5, matching APPROVAL proof metadata/checksums, and Git-indexed approval/review artifacts before dispatch.","proof":["git HEAD is d536210f74b670c1a2a568bd33e40210d9ed9e19 on codex/envctl-package-req026-replay-gate, matching the requested PR head.","generated/task_graph.csv and generated/execution_packets/REQ-027_ENVCTL_REPLAY_ENGINE.json show REQ-027 depends on REQ-021_ENVCTL_TARGET_REGISTRY, REQ-022_ENVCTL_RUN_LEDGER, and REQ-026_ENVCTL_ROLLBACK_CHECKPOINTS, has risk_level=critical, human_approval_required=true, and retains blocked secret/private-key paths.","generated/status_report.json shows REQ-021, REQ-022, and REQ-026 are complete while REQ-027 is pending only under approval_blockers with reason 'agent approval required'.","proof_records/REQ-026_ENVCTL_ROLLBACK_CHECKPOINTS.proof.json shows status=completed, verification_output.status=passed, commands_run included verify_rollback_checkpoints.py and py_compile, failure_reason is empty, and next_action is to run REQ-027 against rollback checkpoint handles.","generated/envctl_rollback_checkpoints_report.json and docs/ENVCTL_ROLLBACK_CHECKPOINTS.md show runtime smoke evidence: 2 checkpoint rows, 2 rollback rows, 1 approval row, 8 event rows, safe rollback succeeded, R4 rollback approval-gated to planned, event_chain.chain_valid=true, and three fail-closed rejection cases.","sha256sum of rollback_checkpoints.py, verify_rollback_checkpoints.py, envctl_rollback_checkpoints_report.json, ENVCTL_ROLLBACK_CHECKPOINTS.md, heartbeat, and log matches the REQ-026 proof checksum bindings for those artifacts.","scripts/goal_loop.py requires approved decision, reviewer/model/summary/evidence, existing review artifact in approved directories, review artifact listed in evidence, fallback_reason for non-Opus reviewers, matching APPROVAL proof status/actor/model/reviewer/decision/evidence/checksums, and git ls-files --cached presence for approval and evidence artifacts.","scripts/agent_approval_gate.py requires fallback_reason when reviewer is not Claude Opus, requires denial instructions for denied decisions, writes the approval artifact, and creates the APPROVAL proof with approval/review evidence and checksum bindings.","docs/AGENT_APPROVAL_GATE.md documents the same fail-closed protocol and explicitly allows GPT-5.5 fallback when Claude Opus is unavailable; current REQ-027 approval/proof artifacts are absent, so dispatch remains blocked until this approval is recorded and staged.","generated/final_verification_report.json reports local_package_complete=true, missing_outputs=[], completed_without_proof=[], unresolved_gaps=[], and only an unrelated documented external Drive-write blocker."],"approved_tasks":["REQ-027_ENVCTL_REPLAY_ENGINE"],"required_changes":[]}
